national institute for occupational safe.data-term: national institute for occupational safety and health

examples.en: He has been deaf since birth.
He's going a little deaf so you'll have to speak up.
examples.ru: Он немного глуховат, так что вам придётся говорить погромче.

examples.en: She's completely deaf in her right ear.
examples.ru: Она полностью глуха на правое ухо.

examples.en: Her muteness was a consequence of her deafness.
Deafness is a frequent concomitant of old age.
